videos.description: Gonzaga's Andrew Nembhard drives and throws a slick over-the-shoulder pass to Drew Timme for the easy layup.
videos.headline: Andrew Nembhard's nice dime sets up Drew Timme for a bucket

videos.description: Alabama's Jaden Shackelford comes up big as he drains a 3-pointer to beat the halftime buzzer to extend its lead to 51-35.
